---
import { siteConfig } from "~/lib/siteConfig";
import { link } from "~/lib/url";
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-navy-800 text-white">
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.25]"
    style="background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at top left, rgba(201,163,90,0.45), transparent 55%), radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom right, rgba(255,255,255,0.10), transparent 55%);"
  >
  </div>

  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 right-[-15%] hidden w-1/2 lg:block"
    style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 65%, rgba(201,163,90,0.25), transparent 60%);"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="container-wide relative grid gap-10 py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-28 lg:grid-cols-12">
    <div class="lg:col-span-7">
      <span class="eyebrow text-gold-300">ES-ES Danışmanlık</span>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-white">
        Doğru Rehberlik,<br />
        Etkili Süreç,<br />
        <span class="text-gold-300">Etkili Sonuç.</span>
      </h1>
      <hr class="gold-divider" />
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-base text-cream-100/85 md:text-lg">
        Öğrencilere ve eğitim kurumlarına yönelik danışmanlık ve mentörlük hizmetleriyle;
        hedeflerinize giden yolda doğru planlama, sürdürülebilir motivasyon ve etkili takip
        sunuyoruz.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap">
        <a href={link("/iletisim#tanisma")} class="btn btn-primary">Ücretsiz Tanışma Görüşmesi</a>
        <a href={link("/hizmetler")} class="btn btn-ghost-light">Hizmetlerimizi İncele</a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-5 text-xs text-cream-200/65">
        Ders, kurs veya etüt vermeyiz; yalnızca danışmanlık ve mentörlük hizmeti sunarız.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="hidden items-center justify-center lg:col-span-5 lg:flex">
      <div class="relative w-full max-w-md">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 -translate-x-6 -translate-y-6 rounded-3xl border border-gold-400/40"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 backdrop-blur">
          <p class="font-serif text-2xl leading-snug text-cream-100">
            <span class="text-gold-300">“</span>
            {siteConfig.brand.subTagline}
            <span class="text-gold-300">”</span>
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 p-4">
              <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gold-300">Yıllarca</p>
              <p class="text-cream-200/80">profesyonel mentörlük deneyimi</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 p-4">
              <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gold-300">Bireysel + Kurumsal</p>
              <p class="text-cream-200/80">iki kanallı danışmanlık</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
